Package: demogendr
Title: Tools for Exploring Democracy and Gender in Political Leadership
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person("Bryce", "Corbett", , "bccorbet@calpoly.edu", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Meghana", "Kolar", , "meghanakolar@gmail.com", role = "aut"),
    person("Julia", "Aptekar", , "japtekar2024@gmail.com", role = "aut"),
    person("Sofia", "Jachno", , "sjach20@gmail.com", role = "aut")) 
Description: A toolkit for exploring how democracy and gender shape
    leadership in governments around the world. It includes a dataset that
    tracks countries year by year, examining their democratic status, the
    leaders who served as presidents or monarchs, and the proportion of
    women holding seats in parliament. The package also provides simple
    functions for loading, summarizing, and visualizing the data.
